    "title_en": "Acoustic Phonon Dynamics in Co-Doped BaFe$_2$As$_2$ Thin Film",
    "abstract_en": "Pump-probe reflectivity reveals coherent acoustic oscillations at 33 and 8.2 GHz in a Ba(Fe$_{0.92}$Co$_{0.08}$)$_2$As$_2$ thin film. The acoustic response was analyzed using a modified logistic-function model, suggesting a temporal redistribution of coherent acoustic energy consistent with anharmonic decay of the higher-frequency mode into the lower-frequency mode.",
